my cat it pooping all over the house my cat has been perfectly fine with pooping in her litter box forever now she started pooping all over the house at night time she only does it some nights but my parents are going to get rid of her if she doesn't stop i really need to know how to get her to stop this is becoming serious to my happiness and my cats life she is only like years old and i don't think she is sick she is acting normal place your cat a clean uncovered litterbox with unscented clumping litter inside a bathroom remove any rugs magazines toys towels etc from the floor remove anything that your cat can push around like litter you can put a water bowl and food dish on the other side of the room from the litter box confine your cat to this room every night until you figure out what the problem is a cat that suddenly stops using her box is saying that something is wrong it could be physical illness fleas or it could be environmental new pet new person etc or it could be the litterbox new cover new smell etc scoop the litter each time she uses it and see if this solves the problem watch her carefully and see if she grooms normally and eats normally a cat that is not feeling well often does not groom very well and may not eat at all excessive purring can also be a sign of stress it is a mystery but you can pinpoint the problem and find a solution Cat Hamster Domestic rabbit Fancy rat Sento Non-Hodgkin's lymphoma Dog Toilet humour Homer Simpson Chinchilla Customs and etiquette of Japan Urinary incontinence Kakapo Friends Kurt Cobain Fire fighting Episodes of Lost (Season 1) The Time Machine Menstrual cup Pitaten Ferret Toxoplasmosis Catscratch Fecal incontinence Flea Kodocha EastEnders Garfield Cannabis cultivation Decompression sickness Phoebe Buffay The Star Wars Holiday Special Litter W.I.T.C.H. Japanese toilet Paris Hilton Cat litter The Shining (film) Theory of conduct Semiconductor device Ron Weasley Shaggy dog story Piccolo Junior Saga Tobacco smoking Equ